<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ( mạtnḥnysẖ fy yạ nfsy wmạtạ̹nysẖ fy
 qwmy bḥmd trjy ạllh ạlḥy ạlsạkn fy )2
 1- ( mktỷbyn lkn msẖ mtḍạyqyn mtḥyryn lkn mạḥnạsẖ yạỷysyn )2
 2- ( mḍṭhdyn lkn msẖ mtrwkyn wmṭrwḥyn lkn mạḥnạsẖ hạlkyn )2
 3- ( kmḍyỷyn lkn ạ̹ḥnạ ṣạdqyn kmjhwlyn lknnạ mʿrwfyn )2
 4- ( kmytyyn lkn ạ̹ḥyạʾ bạdyyn kmw̉dbyn lkn mn ạ̉jl bnyyn )2
 5- ( kmḥzwnyyn lkn bạlrwḥ frḥyn kmḥtạjyn lkn mgẖny ktẖyryn )2</lyrics>
<title>mạtnḥnysẖ fy yạ nfsy</title>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>1557</hymn_number>
</song>